=Description=

"This talk, Trent van Epps - Linux & Ethereum: Commoning vs Commodifying, introduces the concept of digital commons, outlines some parallels between the Linux and Ethereum projects, and how their collective output may become enclosed by commercial entities.

Trent Van Epps works at the Ethereum Foundation on protocol coordination. Member of the [[Protocol Guild]]."


